</div></div>  </div>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-body">        <span class="field-content">We know that the way healthcare is arranged and delivered is important to people and influences their health outcomes
</span>  </span>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-view-node">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/about-planned-care-programme">Read more</a></span>  </span></li>
