</div></div>  </div>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-body">        <span class="field-content">What a patient can expect from the Electives care process, from when a health problem first develops to the time the problem is either resolved or under control.
</span>  </span>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-view-node">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/how-planned-care-process-works">Read more</a></span>  </span></li>
