  <h3 class="field-content">
    <a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/planned-care-interventions">Planned Care Interventions</a>  </h3>
</div></div>  </div>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-body">        <span class="field-content">This data shows the number of Planned Care interventions that were delivered by DHBs for the first two quarters of each of the last three financial years (2017/18, 2018/19, 2019/20) and full year data for each of the last five calendar years.
</span>  </span>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-view-node">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/planned-care-interventions">Read more</a></span>  </span></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even">  
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <div class="field-content">
