</div></div>  </div>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-body">        <span class="field-content">Answers to commonly asked&nbsp;questions about what to expect from the Planned Care services process.
</span>  </span>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-view-node">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/questions-and-answers-planned-care-services">Read more</a></span>  </span></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd views-row-last">  
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <div class="field-content">
