</div></div>  </div>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-body">        <span class="field-content">DHBs have certain requirements for providing Planned Care services
</span>  </span>  
  <span class="views-field views-field-view-node">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/hospitals-and-specialist-care/planned-care-services/planned-care-services-and-how-dhbs-are-performing">Read more</a></span>  </span></li>
      </ul></div>    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
